title: Treasury Long-Term Average (25 years and above) (DISCONTINUED)
notes: Based on the unweighted average of the bid yields for all Treasury fixed-coupon securities with remaining terms to maturity of 25 years and over. Averages of business days. For further information, please refer to http://www.federalreserve.gov/releases/h15/treas_long-term_rate_discontinuence.htm.
